@baseUrl = http://localhost:5029/api
@adminEmail = admin@casezero.com
@adminPassword = CaseZero123!

### 1. Login para obter token de admin
# @name adminLogin
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "{{adminEmail}}",
  "password": "{{adminPassword}}"
}

### 2. Listar casos existentes
GET {{baseUrl}}/cases
Authorization: Bearer {{adminLogin.response.body.token}}

### 3. Criar um novo caso básico (apenas com nome)
POST {{baseUrl}}/cases
Authorization: Bearer {{adminLogin.response.body.token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Caso Teste Básico",
  "titleEn": "Basic Test Case",
  "description": "Caso criado para testar o sistema sem arquivos ou evidências",
  "descriptionEn": "Case created to test the system without files or evidence",
  "difficulty": 1,
  "estimatedTimeMinutes": 30,
  "isPublished": true,
  "location": "Teste",
  "locationEn": "Test"
}

### 4. Listar casos novamente para ver o novo caso
GET {{baseUrl}}/cases
Authorization: Bearer {{adminLogin.response.body.token}}

### 5. Obter detalhes do caso recém-criado (substitua {ID} pelo ID retornado)
GET {{baseUrl}}/cases/3
Authorization: Bearer {{adminLogin.response.body.token}}

### 6. Verificar evidências do caso (deve estar vazia)
GET {{baseUrl}}/evidence/case/3
Authorization: Bearer {{adminLogin.response.body.token}}
